OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in property
OL,6,FA murder investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched after a woman died at a
OL,8,Fproperty in Caldicot.
OL,10,FGwent Police were called to Green
OL,11,FLane, Caldicot, at around 3am on
OL,12,FThursday, June 4, after reports that a
OL,13,Fwoman was found unresponsive at an
OL,14,Faddress on the street.
OL,16,FParamedics from the Welsh Ambulance
OL,17,FService attended alongside police and
OL,18,Fa 52-year-old woman from Caldicot was
OL,19,Fpronounced dead at the scene.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
