OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780596668
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in property
OL,6,FThe force said her family have been
OL,7,Finformed and are being supported by
OL,8,Fspecialist officers.
OL,10,FA 50-year-old man from Caldicot has
OL,11,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of murder
OL,12,Fand is currently in police custody.
OL,14,FSenior investigating officer,
OL,15,FDetective Chief Inspector Matthew
OL,16,FClarke said: "We would like to
OL,17,Freassure the communities of Caldicot
OL,18,Fthat we are doing everything we can to
OL,19,Festablish the circumstances
OL,20,Fsurrounding the victim's death.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
