OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780596668
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in property
OL,6,F"We understand that reports of this
OL,7,Fnature can cause concern, however we
OL,8,Fhave arrested a man from the area who
OL,9,Fwas known to the victim, and we are
OL,10,Fnot looking for anyone else in
OL,11,Fconnection with this incident.
OL,13,F"Residents may see an increased number
OL,14,Fof officers in the area as we carry
OL,15,Fout further enquiries. We encourage
OL,16,Fanyone with information to please
OL,17,Fspeak with one of our officers, or
OL,18,Fcontact us on the usual channels."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
