OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780596668
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cwoman found dead in property
OL,6,FOfficers are appealing for anyone with
OL,7,Finformation to come forward,
OL,8,Fparticularly residents who live on
OL,9,FGreen Lane and Cae Mawr Road who may
OL,10,Fhave heard anything unusual in the
OL,11,Fearly hours of the morning of Thursday
OL,12,F4 June.
OL,14,FAnyone with any information is asked
OL,15,Fto contact police quoting log
OL,16,Freference 2600174602.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
